  "instructions": [
    "Heat 1 tablespoon of vegetable oil in a large skillet or wok over medium-high heat.",
    "Add the sliced onion and bell pepper and cook until tender, about 3-4 minutes.",
    "Add the beef and cook until browned, about 3-4 minutes.",
    "Add the Korean chili flakes, gochujang, soy sauce, brown sugar, garlic, and ginger. Stir to combine.",
